title: The worst!!!
review: The only reason that I rated this 'movie' a 1 (awful), is because there is no zero (0) rating.  If ever you want to ruin a perfect evening , or better yet, you desire to get rid of annoying company, I suggest you have this 'movie' on hand.  I found this 'movie' to be more distressing than the flu, and more annoying than a pesky ex-girlfriend.
